VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT danger_accept_invalid_certs\(\s*true\s*\)|danger_accept_invalid_hostnames\(\s*true\s*\)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:test|development|localhost|staging
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects TLS certificate/hostname validation bypass in Rust HTTP clients.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Actix Insecure TLS Handling.
